<eesti> arvutamisel kasutatava aasta pikkus on 365 p&auml;eva v&otilde;i 365,25 p&auml;eva v&otilde;i (liigaasta) 366 p&auml;eva, 52 n&auml;dalat v&otilde;i 12 v&otilde;rdset kuud; arvutamisel kasutatava v&otilde;rdse kuu pikkus on 30, 41666 p&auml;eva; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it is desirable that consumers should be able to recognize the terms used different Member States to indicate the 'annual percentage rate of charge'; </inglise>
